10/20/2024,748.311(11) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,11/08/2024,11/06/2024,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,No,The serious incident report for an unauthorized absence of a child in care did not include an update upon the child's return. ,"On 11/6/2024, the operation's Administrator advised Blessed Kidz RTC will ensure all staff are trained to report and document serious incidents as it relates to unauthorized absences as well as updates to such reports upon their return. Training documented by certificate."
10/20/2024,748.303(a)(10)(A) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,11/08/2024,11/06/2024,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,No,Licensing was not notified of a child's absence from the operation. Immediate notification is required due to the child's trafficking history. ,"On 11/6/2024, the operation's Administrator advised Blessed Kidz RTC will ensure all staff are trained to report and document serious incidents as it relates to unauthorized absence to licensing no later than 6 hours after determining unauthorized absence of a child 13 years old or older. If a child is suspected of or was a trafficking victim, the unauthorized absence will be reported immediately. Training documented by certificate."
