10/20/2024,748.507(1) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,11/08/2024,11/06/2024,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium High,No,"A child, with identified trafficking history, admitted to having a sexual encounter with a person after an unauthorized absence from the operation was not taken to be seen by medical personnel. ","On 11/6/2024, the operation's Administrator advised Blessed Kidz RTC will ensure that all staff receive training on competency, prudent judgment and self-control in the presence of children and when performing assigned tasks. Upon return from an unauthorized absence, if a child discloses that she has had sexual intercourse, a provider will be found that can assess her within a week. Training documented by certificate."
